PLP
(Practice|Learn|Play)
UNLIMITED range balls, any day, any time.
FREE golf instruction twice weekly by PGA Golf Professionals.
7-day advance booking tee time window.
REDUCE afternoon course fees and an INCLUDED draft beer or soda when you play.
For more detailed information, please see our info sheets. Question? Email us at
This email address is being protected from spambots. You need JavaScript enabled to view it.
Summer Loyalty Program
"Simply the best value IN-SEASON golf program on the Treasure Coast!"
Only $50! Summer Rates EVERYDAY from May 1st through September 30th!
